5:
We can't even get a break during

9:
Their skills are also getting better.
We're basically fighting soldiers at

14:
Is this the work of those guys
Yakumo beat up last time?
21:
Show yourselves. Or should I drag
you out myself?
25:
You betrayed the shogunate just like

27:
That may be the case, but I will
never sink down to your level.
29:
But you're also looking for Orochi,

34:
Tell us what you seek. Whatever it is,

42:
You will not lay a single finger on

46:
Yakumo! Calm down, they can't hurt
us anymore!
51:
Remember, Suizen's counting on us!
We need to arrest and send them

61:
...Sorry about that. But I can't stand
listening to these traitors any longer.
68:
What's this? Aramasa and Karasahi
just vibrated.
70: That blade... Is that from Orochi?
79:
You said you're still looking for that
girl, right? How about giving this a

84:
I'm not quite sure I understand, but

93:
What do we have here? I sensed a

102:
The vibrations from before... Wait a
minute, do these blades look

106:
Their aura... No doubt about it; it

108:
Tell me, child. Who did you
encounter with these blades?
111:
...Let's start from the beginning, shall
we?
123:
I was given orders from the
shogunate to hunt down the last of
the Grand Diviner's spies.
124:
They were trying to bring Orochi
back into this world.
126:
I struck them down, but one by one
each of them offered themselves to
Orochi. Until they were successful in

130:
After it was all over, there was a girl...
wrapped in light.
131:
Sensing that it was a vengeful spirit,
Aramasa and Karasahi urged me to
attack.
133:
I didn't hesitate. I gripped my swords
and went for the strike.
136:
...It was a direct hit. My blades
pierced right through her body.
150:
...No doubt about it, there is a sense
of nostalgia emitting from those
blades of yours.
153:
But I am afraid that all of my
previous partners are long gone by

154:
If that is so, then that leaves only
one conclusion; that entity must be

162:
It means it is not "human". If it
manifests in the presence of hate
and rage, then you may be dealing
with a vengeful spirit.
170:
A vengeful spirit... But... I want to
meet her... I NEED to see her. And I
won't let anyone get in my way.
173: Even if that means you, Alk...
183:
You're not planning on BECOMING a
vengeful spirit, are you?
186: If not, then you can count on us!
195:
I am curious though. What do you
plan on doing once you meet this
spirit?
199: I-I haven't thought that far ahead...
202:
I've never felt this way before... How
do I find what it is I truly desire?
206:
Ahaha. The answer lies within
yourself, child. In due time, it will find
you.
209:
In the meantime, you have my
support as well.
212:
Remember this. The greatest
hurdles in life can always be
overcome with what lies within.
217:
...I wonder if I truly will find it when I
meet her.
